'''全国公共广播电台'''（{{lang-en|'''National Public Radio'''}}，[[缩写|缩写]]为'''{{lang|en|NPR}}'''）是[[美國|美國]]一家获公众[[赞助|赞助]]及部分[[政府|政府]]资助、但独立运作的非商业性[[美国媒体|媒體機構]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/about-npr/178660742/public-radio-finances|title=Public Radio Finances|work=NPR|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219042754/https://www.npr.org/about-npr/178660742/public-radio-finances|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2012/10/10/why-exactly-should-the-government-fund-pbs-and-npr/|title=Why exactly should the government fund PBS and NPR?|work=Washington Post|date=2012-10-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cpb.org/aboutpb/faq/cpbpbsnpr.html|title=What is the difference between CPB, PBS & NPR?|work=CPB|accessdate=2015-04-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150511193653/http://www.cpb.org/aboutpb/faq/cpbpbsnpr.html|archivedate=2015-05-11}}</ref>，成立於1970年2月24日，開播於1971年4月<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/about-npr/192827079/overview-and-history|title=Overview and History|work=NPR|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219084807/https://www.npr.org/about-npr/192827079/overview-and-history|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NPR_at_50/>。其以[[廣播聯賣|廣播聯賣]]的方式為全美約9百間{{link-en|NPR成員台列表|List of NPR stations|公共廣播電台}}提供節目，以[[新闻|新闻]]、综述、采访为主，也有一些[[音乐|音乐]]、[[談話節目|脱口秀]]等[[文化|文化]]、[[娱乐|娱乐]]节目。2009年时，[[听众|听众]]数目已超过2000万人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/03/23/AR2009032302972.html|title=Good News for NPR: Its Most Listeners Ever|work=Washington Post|accessdate=2015-04-16|date=2009-03-24|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725111409/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/03/23/AR2009032302972.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

